The evidence with the title 'What are the statistics on human trafficking of children? ' says Jul 31, 2017  ... International human trafficking of children statistics compiled by Ark Of Hope  ... 300,000 Americans under 18 are lured into the commercial sex trade every  ... Average victims age is 11 to 14 ; approx 80 % are women and children  ... Children trafficked in the United States is actually much higher than 300,000 . 
